                  </persName> was indicted<rs id="t18450203-473-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18450203-473-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18450203-473-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing 7 pairs of boots, value 10<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18450203-name-406" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18450203-name-406" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
